reviewText: If you know your bible these are ok to watch.
Great set and fact filled stories with great production!
Did not like it at all. Thought I was ordering the Bible series, but this wasn't it.
Great DVD collection.  Lots of information to process.  I spend time reading my Bible reinforcing the DVD content.  Money well soent.

My best friend and I have both watched this set of DVD's separated.  We DVD's provided so much additional information clarifying parts of the bible for both of us.  The set is awesome and would make a wonderful Christmas present to any Christian.
